# Workflow

1. Summarize commit message
2. Stage all files

# Template

<type>(<scope>): <subject>

# Common types (type):

feat ✨ New feature
fix 🐛 Bug fix
docs 📝 Documentation changes
style 💄 Code style adjustments
refactor ♻️ Refactor (neither adding features nor fixing bugs)
perf ⚡ Performance optimization
test ✅ Add or modify tests
chore 🔧 Build tools / dependency updates / script changes
revert ⏪ Revert commit
ci 🛠️ CI/CD configuration changes
build 📦 Build-related changes

# Example:

feat(login): add user login feature
